ğŸ”§ Troubleshooting
Problem	Possible Cause	Solution
Invalid date format	Wrong input format	Use YYYY-MM-DD
Crashes on startup	Missing storage file	Run any command to create it
Status/priority errors	Invalid values passed	Use valid enum values
Changes not saved	Direct object mutation	Always call save() after changes
Logging / Debugging

You can add extra print statements or integrate logging for better visibility.

